opennlp.ccg.lexicon
Class LicensingFeature

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.lexicon.LicensingFeature

public class LicensingFeature
extends Object

A licensing feature is one which controls the licensing and instantiation of semantically null or marked categories in the realizer. Defaults are handled in Lexicon.loadLicensingFeatures.

Version:
$Revision: 1.7 $, $Date: 2009/12/21 03:27:18 $
Author:
Michael White
